{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">知道刻度尺</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是测量长度的常用工具；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会使用刻度尺测量长度；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">初步了解误差。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">刻度尺</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是测量长度的常用工具</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">刻度尺、三角板、长方形物块、球形物块。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.观察</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">你所选用的刻度尺的量程</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分度值。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.用刻度尺测量物体长度。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.将测量结果记入下表。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size:13px; text-align:justify; width:356px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:169px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量对象</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:187px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量对象</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:169px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">长方体</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:187px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:169px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小球</span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:187px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">刻度尺要平行于被测物体放置，有刻度的一边要紧贴被测物体；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">读数时视线要与尺面垂直；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">读数时注意估读；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记录时要注明单位。</span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量较小物体时，可以采取化少为多的方法，如：测</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">张纸的厚度时可以先测</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">张纸的厚度，再除以</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量曲线长度时可以采取化曲为直的方法，如：测量圆的周长时可以先用细线绕圆一周，再将线拉直，测量细线长度。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}